Installation instructions for ARCLibrary Extension v1.0
-------------------------------------------------------

In the following instructions we will use the abbreviation ALE for LinkedData 
Extension.


Requirements: 
=============

    MediaWiki 1.15.x
    Deployment Framework (optional, but recommended for a fast and easy installation)

Installation:
=============

How to install with deployment framework:

(1) Download the Deployment Framework
(2) Extract the Deployment Framework zip-file into the MediaWiki roots folder
(3) Open the SMWAdministration tool
(4) Type 'smwadmin -i arclibrary'
    This installs the extension.

How to install manually:

(1) Install ALE which you can find at 
    http://
(2) Extract the files into a folder named ARCLibrary.
(2) Copy this folder into the extensions folder of MediaWiki. 
(3) Activate the ALE by adding the following lines to LocalSettings.php: 
	include_once('extensions/ARCLibrary/ARCLibrary.php');
	enableARCLibrary(); 


